Uses of Class
org.eclipse.gef4.layout.LayoutContext

  • Packages that use LayoutContext 
    Package Description
    org.eclipse.gef4.layout
    This package provides an interface-based facade to exchange layout information with layout algorithms (within this package), concrete implementations of layout algorithms ( org.eclipse.gef4.layout.algorithms).
    org.eclipse.gef4.layout.algorithms
    This package provides different implementations of concrete layout algorithms.
